00:02:15.318 --> 00:02:19.141
computer around and can read the
text because I want you to look

00:02:19.141 --> 00:02:22.538
at the text as we're talking
about it on Wednesday,

00:02:22.538 --> 00:02:24.318
just like I want you to look at
